    {
      "content": "After running the experiment, you can click on the output port of the [Evaluate Model][evaluate-model] module and select <bpt id=\"p1\">*</bpt>Visualize<ept id=\"p1\">*</ept> to see the evaluation results.",
      "pos": [
        4464,
